{"tid":1051602,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"週末出租朋友現正開放報名！反應熱烈！額滿即止！","createTime":"2019-03-07T17:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-07T17:41:21.000Z","uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fdebb23c9de4a7341f227f45557e88df7642be0e","tid":1051602,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"好快又到一週一度既星期六日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位毒撚毒絲見到人地有朋友👫👫👫<br />\n係咪好想身邊都有個朋友 陪你一齊過呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n機會黎啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想搵大隻靚仔型撚浮雲哥做出租朋友既你 已經冇時間再猶疑 即刻報名啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n💲💲收費表💲💲<br />\n請我食飯=$100<br />\n請我睇戲=$150<br />\n同我傾計=$1/10隻字<br />\n一齊行街=$20/分鐘<br />\n<br />\n靚仔或靚女九折<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大隻靚仔或大波靚女半價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n教到我溝女免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根據過往經驗 每星期反應都非常熱烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要報名就快手啦 遲左又要等一個禮拜架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位都有個開開心心既週末<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c21903622796a6e3aacc561066629f24885cd0c6","tid":1051602,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:15:29.000Z","msg":"@水果糖水"},{"pid":"2ba42f6f0aebbabb8a80ff9fd9ddd15ad32cc2e1","tid":1051602,"uid":63291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:17:46.000Z","msg":"點解睇戲貴過食飯"},{"pid":"7296fbcb5fb065f305325eeca8183e4f8f85a425","tid":1051602,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"大隻靚仔型撚浮雲哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba18ecb7b672ecc6b5b6c07df8276b8a578df59","tid":1051602,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba42f6f0aebbabb8a80ff9fd9ddd15ad32cc2e1","tid":1051602,"uid":63291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:17:46.000Z","msg":"點解睇戲貴過食飯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"因為可以食貴野"},{"pid":"85e26680e87ce78509d96f48ad0cde5702852864","tid":1051602,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7296fbcb5fb065f305325eeca8183e4f8f85a425","tid":1051602,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"大隻靚仔型撚浮雲哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"唔可以非禮我"},{"pid":"604bcf31463edc458c8bfcf2f7d51ce22faca1b9","tid":1051602,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T17:23:02.000Z","msg":"。。。又發癲"},{"pid":"c7cccfe2eff1b4c76fba740b6ea88fa54a487923","tid":1051602,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"604bcf31463edc